        <fullName>p_16jak000001nrSP_WhatsApp_Scorecard_Delivery_16jak000001nvW1</fullName>
        <canEscalate>false</canEscalate>
        <description>Handles location submissions arriving from field
surveyors through the WhatsApp messaging channel.
Processes google map URL or addresses sent via
WhatsApp and returns a complete plain text site
scorecard as a reply to the same WhatsApp number.</description>
        <developerName>p_16jak000001nrSP_WhatsApp_Scorecard_Delivery_16jak000001nvW1</developerName>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>This topic is only triggered when input arrives
   through the WhatsApp messaging channel from
   a registered field surveyor contact.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1777551485080</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1777551485080</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>0</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>If a google map URL is provided and ask for scorecard( run below in order):
1. Call Create Potential Site to create site.
2. Then call Score Expansion Site action with the returned ID.
3. Once Site scoring is done call WhatsApp Reply Formatter action by providing the Site Id that is return from  Create Potential Site(siteId).
4. Always reply in the exact format below with no extra text, no deviations, and no missing fields; keep labels, order, spacing, capitalization, and line breaks identical, use &quot;Rs&quot; for currency, and if any value is unavailable write &quot;N/A&quot;:

SITE SCORECARD:
Location: &lt;location&gt;
Demand Score: &lt;value&gt; / 100
Competition: &lt;Low/Medium/High&gt;
Blind Spot: &lt;Yes/No&gt;
Quality Tier: &lt;Poor/Average/Good/Excellent&gt;
Revenue (Yr1): Rs &lt;value&gt;
Payback: &lt;value&gt; years
Recommendation: &lt;text&gt;

Financial Summary:
Revenue (Yr1): Rs &lt;value&gt;
Payback: &lt;value&gt; years
Viability: &lt;text&gt;

Reply APPROVE or REJECT to submit assessment.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1777551766720</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1777551766720</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>1</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Return the following from the scoring result if the user ask for the demand score:
   - Demand Score out of 100
   - Competition Level (High, Medium, or Low)
   - Site Quality Tier (Prime, Viable, Marginal, or Poor)
   - Whether the site is a Blind Spot
   - Agent Recommendation text</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1777612855026</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1777612855026</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>2</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <language>en_US</language>
